* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
* cplay is just a front-end; to use it, you need to install one or more *
* of the following ports (audio players):                               *
*                                                                       *
*   audio/madplay                                                       *
*   audio/mikmod                                                        *
*   audio/mpg123                                                        *
*   audio/mpg321                                                        *
*   audio/sox                                                           *
*   audio/speex                                                         *
*   audio/splay                                                         *
*   audio/vorbis-tools                                                  *
*   audio/xmp                                                           *
*   multimedia/mplayer                                                  *
*   multimedia/mpv                                                      *
*                                                                       *
* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
